OL,3,CParish meetings 'will die' unless more
OL,4,Cpeople attend, politician warns
OL,6,FA Jersey politician has warned that
OL,7,Fthe island's parish assemblies risk
OL,8,F'dying' if attendances do not improve.
OL,10,FRichard Vibert, the Connetable for St
OL,11,FPeter, told ITV News that low turnout
OL,12,Fand engagement must be addressed.
OL,14,FSpeaking at a public meeting with an
OL,15,Fattendance of just 25, he added:
OL,16,F"People don't understand what the
OL,17,Fparish assembly is actually doing.
