OL,3,CParish meetings 'will die' unless more
OL,4,Cpeople attend, politician warns
OL,6,F"We advertise the meetings online,
OL,7,Femail parishioners, put them in the
OL,8,Fpaper, and post about them on the
OL,9,Fparish notice board - they have all
OL,10,Fhad the opportunity to attend if they
OL,11,Fwanted to.
OL,13,F"We have to address this, otherwise it
OL,14,Fwill die."
OL,16,FIn St Ouen, residents raised concerns
OL,17,Fover how representative the parish
OL,18,Fassembly's decision-making was, after
OL,19,F20 members elected to spend up to
OL,20,F#16,000 of ratepayers' money on
OL,21,Freplacing road signs.
