OL,3,CParish meetings 'will die' unless more
OL,4,Cpeople attend, politician warns
OL,6,FSimon Crowcroft, the Connetable of St
OL,7,FHelier, has suggested that the timings
OL,8,Fof parish assembly meetings could set
OL,9,Fthem up for failure.
OL,11,FHe explained: "Parish assemblies tend
OL,12,Fto take place in the evening, which is
OL,13,Fnot convenient for a lot of people.
OL,15,F"During COVID, we managed to have
OL,16,Fonline meetings, but it's quite
OL,17,Fdifficult to ensure that online voting
OL,18,Ffor these happens in a proper way.
