OL,3,CParish meetings 'will die' unless more
OL,4,Cpeople attend, politician warns
OL,6,F"There is some way to go to make sure
OL,7,Fthese meetings are more accessible to
OL,8,Fthe public."
OL,10,FConnetable Crowcroft, who is Jersey's
OL,11,Flongest-serving politician and is
OL,12,Fstanding down at June's election,
OL,13,Fadded that the Parish of St Helier had
OL,14,Ftried to livestream meetings, a
OL,15,Fpractice commonly used across the
OL,16,FBritish Isles during the pandemic, but
OL,17,Ffailed to attract sufficient viewers
OL,18,Fto make it worthwhile.
