OL,3,CParish meetings 'will die' unless more
OL,4,Cpeople attend, politician warns
OL,6,FJackie Weaver, who rose to fame after
OL,7,Fa video of her trying to mediate an
OL,8,Fonline Handforth Parish Council
OL,9,Fmeeting went viral, believes that
OL,10,Fmaking parish assemblies more
OL,11,Faccessible would boost their
OL,12,Fpopularity.
OL,14,FShe said: "I can't think of any
OL,15,Fdisadvantages to online meetings, it's
OL,16,Fso frustrating that they haven't
OL,17,Fautomatically been adopted in the UK."
