OL,4,Cpeople attend, politician warns
OL,6,FMs Weaver continued: "During COVID,
OL,7,Fall of the people who didn't normally
OL,8,Fhave time to travel to lofty buildings
OL,9,Fin their busy lives could access
OL,10,Fcouncils and their decision-making
OL,11,Fprocesses much more easily online.
OL,13,F"There's no point sitting in a town
OL,14,Fhall waiting for everyone to come to
OL,15,Fyou; committees have to go to where
OL,16,Fpeople are, which, particularly for
OL,17,Fyoung people, is online and on social
OL,18,Fmedia."
